{"word":"H85 - אַבְרָהָם - ʼAbrâhâm - ab-raw-hawm' - Abraham","slug":"H85","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אַבְרָהָם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼAbrâhâm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ab-raw-hawm'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abraham"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>אברהם</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>'abrâhâm</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ab-raw-hawm'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Abraham = \"father of a multitude\" or \" chief of multitude\" <ol><li>friend of God and founder of Hebrew nation via God's elective covenant</li></ol> <p />Origin: contracted from <a href=\"#/H1\">H1</a> and an unused root (probably meaning to be populous) <p />TWOT entry: <a class=\"T\" href=\"S:0004 - 'bh\">4b</a> <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1\">H1</a>, <a href=\"#/H21\">H21</a>, <a href=\"#/H22\">H22</a>, <a href=\"#/H23\">H23</a>, <a href=\"#/H26\">H26</a>, <a href=\"#/H27\">H27</a>, <a href=\"#/H28\">H28</a>, <a href=\"#/H29\">H29</a>, <a href=\"#/H30\">H30</a>, <a href=\"#/H31\">H31</a>, <a href=\"#/H32\">H32</a>, <a href=\"#/H33\">H33</a>, <a href=\"#/H36\">H36</a>, <a href=\"#/H37\">H37</a>, <a href=\"#/H372\">H372</a>, <a href=\"#/H373\">H373</a>, <a href=\"#/H38\">H38</a>, <a href=\"#/H39\">H39</a>, <a href=\"#/H40\">H40</a>, <a href=\"#/H41\">H41</a>, <a href=\"#/H42\">H42</a>, <a href=\"#/H43\">H43</a>, <a href=\"#/H44\">H44</a>, <a href=\"#/H45\">H45</a>, <a href=\"#/H48\">H48</a>, <a href=\"#/H49\">H49</a>, <a href=\"#/H50\">H50</a>, <a href=\"#/H51\">H51</a>, <a href=\"#/H52\">H52</a>, <a href=\"#/H53\">H53</a>, <a href=\"#/H54\">H54</a>, <a href=\"#/H74\">H74</a>, <a href=\"#/H87\">H87</a>"}]}